HEADWORD: Spit curl
<hw>Spit" curl`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A little lock of hair, plastered
in a spiral form on the temple or forehead with spittle, or other
adhesive substance.</def> <mark>[Colloq.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

